TO: MAX REINHARDT

CC, 1 p.

Ithaca, N.Y.





January 26, 1959

Dear Mr. Reinhardt,

I am very much moved by Mr. Graham Greene's attitude toward my book. Will you please convey to him my deepest gratitude.

